description: Welcome to 655 E 2nd Street #202, a stunning penthouse in South Boston. This spacious 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom home boasts newly upgraded hardwood floors, kitchen cabinets, and countertops. High ceilings and abundant natural light enhance the open floor plan, while a gas fireplace adds a cozy touch to this urban sanctuary.The apartment offers ample storage, including custom outfitted closets in each bedroom, 2 additional closets in the living area, and a laundry closet with a vented washer and dryer. 2 spacious bathrooms including an en-suite bathroom in the primary w/ double vanity. An additional deeded storage closet is conveniently located on the same floor. The oversized heated garage space ensures easy and convenient parking. Situated in the eastern section of South Boston, this home is close to Seaport, W Broadway, beaches, restaurants, shopping, parks, and the forthcoming Edison Power Plant development, which is slated to offer features like new parks, retail, restaurants and more.
